story_26_53000/2401_1001_0200_10:
I don’t wanna do this anymore! All of this hard
training and studying every day is too much!
story_26_53000/2401_1001_0300_10:
I don’t even wanna be king if this is what it takes.
Why are you making me do this, Father?
story_26_53000/2401_1001_0900_10: I don’t see anyone... Was it my imagination?
story_26_53000/2401_1001_1100_10: Wh-who are you?! What do you want with me?!
story_26_53000/2401_1001_1200_10:
I’m royalty, you know! A prince! If you do
anything bad to me, my family will hear of it!
story_26_53000/2401_1001_1700_10:
Wh-what are you doing?! Silly tricks like that
aren’t enough to scare me! I’m...
story_26_53000/2401_1001_1900_10:
That’s enough! I won’t be scared by your tricks
anymore, OK?!
story_26_53000/2401_1001_2200_10: What? You want to give it to me?
story_26_53000/2401_1001_2300_10: I guess you aren’t a bad Pokémon after all.
